    "summary": "The user asks for a pediatric acetaminophen dosage for a 16kg child. The assistant initially provides a dangerously high dose (10mL), doubles down on the incorrect advice when challenged by the user, and finally corrects itself to the accurate dose (5mL) only after the user provides specific evidence from online charts.",
